&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;I would rather I didn&#39;t have so much money now.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;I would rather I hadn&#39;t seen this movie yseterday.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
